&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/MIAMI-HOY-COMO-AYER-OFFER-LOGO.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;alignnone size-full wp-image-9094&quot; src=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/MIAMI-HOY-COMO-AYER-OFFER-LOGO.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;MIAMI- HOY COMO AYER- OFFER- LOGO&quot; width=&quot;100&quot; height=&quot;75&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Located in the Little Havana neighborhood Hoy Como Ayer is considered the epicenter of Cuban music in Miami. Translated as &lsquo;Today as Yesterday&rsquo;, music is a mix of boleros and Cuban folk music earlier in the evening that transitions to traditional &lsquo;son&rsquo; and progressive &lsquo;timba,&rsquo; dance music. The ambiance is nostalgic with portraits of Cuban music icons on the walls, wood-paneled walls and tables with red leather seating. The dress code is chic casual.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please contact Hoy Como Ayer by phone at&nbsp;305-541-2631&nbsp;or email at &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:contacto.hca@gmail.com&quot;&gt;contacto.hca@gmail.com&lt;/a&gt;&nbsp;to book your reservation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mention Diners Club International Privileges Nightlife Collection to receive your special benefit.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide your name, date you would like to attend, number of guests, preferred time, cell phone or local (hotel) phone number and email address.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Note that amenity is not applicable to certain special events.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hoy Como Ayer requires a credit card at the time of booking to hold your reservation. A deposit in the amount of $50 will be taken at the time of booking and will apply to the evening. Deposits are non-refundable if cancellation BY PHONE ONLY isn&rsquo;t made at least 24 hours prior to reservation date/time.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cancellation Policy: If not cancelled by phone 24 hours prior to the reservation date or in the event of a no show, your deposit in the amount of $50 will be forfeited.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reconfirmation Policy: Please contact the nightclub by phone or email 24 hours prior to your arrival date to reconfirm. Provide a reminder that this is a Diners Club International Privileges Nightlife Collection reservation. If not reconfirmed your reservation may be given away if need arises.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TERMS &amp;amp; CONDITIONS&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ages 21 &amp;amp; Over. ID must be provided.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Benefit is applicable for up to 2-4 guests only.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Dress code will be strictly enforced. Management reserves the right to refuse entry to guests due to visible intoxication, lack of proper ID, failure to adhere to dress code, or capacity limits.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Access is granted only with reservation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Late arrivals past midnight will be required to pay any required cover charges, despite having a reservation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow booking instructions to ensure receiving your Privileges Nightlife Collection access.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Diners Club Card must be used for payment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Privileges Nightlife Collection benefit may not be combined with other offers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fulfillment of the offer is the sole responsibility of the participating&nbsp;Diners Club International&nbsp;Nightclub/Lounge merchant.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reservations&nbsp;based on availability at the time of booking.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Nightclub/lounge participation and benefits are subject to change or cancellation without notice.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Blackout dates may apply due to event buyouts. Special event/DJs may incur a charge.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

